I really hate the way I created 2014 for myself.  I can't believe I was like that.  Seriously, I love this guy, PewDiePie.  He's the king of YouTube for the right reasons; however, looking back at this vid now, I feel ashamed for myself; and I'm sorry for negatively fueling and impacting the ones who read those comments.
